      "text": "三十分後にスタジオでオーディション開始や",
      "startTime": 77.3666460675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三十分後",
      "startTime": 81.5961017609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「あれは……うさぎが喋りながら走ってる……？」",
      "startTime": 83.5961037954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ダメ……もっと大きな声で感情を込めて言わないと……",
      "startTime": 88.8666688283,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5354.965782299999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "雫ちゃん、もうすぐオーディションの時間やけど",
